{"id": 1693, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都被无孔不入的广告逼成啥样了？", "description": "连强迫症都已经被强迫治好了啊。", "record_count": 16537, "comment_count": 62, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170517102826FuPj4wxI2ALebkJH.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-17T17:00:56Z", "questions": [{"id": 2341, "title": "你都被无孔不入的广告逼成啥样了？", "content": "你都被无孔不入的广告逼成啥样了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 204321, "content": "手机app的小红点，以前要全点掉，现在打开来找一圈都不知道在哪点掉", "image": "img/option/option/20170517094138ZuoXOPbA5xI0QeNa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204322, "content": "收到短信广告，能快速识别应该回“N”“TD”还是“TD退订”", "image": "img/option/option/20170517094421NwpEAOleLgt8XDVu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204323, "content": "但即使回了退订，它们换个号继续发，现在都放着不管了", "image": "img/option/option/20170517093812KgVxIcXOmshPUAlf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204324, "content": "记得常看的公众号第几条是广告，标题再诱人也跳过不看", "image": "img/option/option/20170517094330vR3ALD49JlTMhbj6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204325, "content": "外卖开盒的前一个步骤是，把要看的剧集打开来放广告", "image": "img/option/option/20170517101952dK4ea7imyLxsO80q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204326, "content": "放广告的时候忍住不点全屏（其实是广告详情）", "image": "img/option/option/20170517094702smCPgqBGlwYT5jxH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204328, "content": "微博广告点了无数次“不感兴趣”仍然出现在时间线上，只能淡定划过", "image": "img/option/option/201705171019324xU7LHuKTViQW0nX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 204329, "content": "app开屏广告，点跳过点不准反倒打开广告了，现在就放任它放完", "image": "img/option/option/20170517094301bZDu4SG86OotwYdX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}